{"tid":531501,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"宋康昊曾被稱為「韓國周星馳」, 現在卻青出於藍","createTime":"2018-01-17T01:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T02:45:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4649bf0dcc7cc979991451f639e9ad2f52fc12","tid":531501,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"記得宋康昊出道時, 曾被稱為「韓國周星馳」 ;  而周星馳仲曾經因為十分欣賞宋康昊, 而為《茅躉王》配音.<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/34863.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.sina.com.cn%2Fm%2Ff%2F34863.html&d=L34AUgwE3moM9iudM2%2FtZgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ea88a0d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/34863.html</a><br />\n<br />\n但而家, 不能不認宋康昊已超過周星馳. 因為宋康昊肯跳出Comfort zone, 演出不同類型既電影同角色:《復仇》、《殺人回憶》、《饑渴誘罪》、《逆權大狀》、《逆權司機》呢類電影, 周星馳一世都唔敢演.  但因為宋康昊既膽色, 令佢成為一位全面演員.<br />\n<br />\n反而, 周星馳跳不出自己的Comfort zone, 電影和演出都愈黎愈差. (佢係《長江7號》演出都好差, 完全唔似一位基層工人.  反而宋康昊係《逆權司機》就真係演活左一位基層的士司機.)"},{"pid":"bc4e0a0e48be11ef98e31abec8eefa46fa7fc144","tid":531501,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩"},{"pid":"99e72845363f2894c50327368215326242658373","tid":531501,"uid":6436,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢韓國周星馳，我有幾可拍笑片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c83bb51eb501902f7a5c36d19cfc657444d0a1","tid":531501,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"20年後仲有電視台重播先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89622dcf067f8f89ad204c6e1a554f3ad168e8bc","tid":531501,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"唔認同周星馳冇跳出comfort zone喎<br />\n佢只係跳出個效果差啫"}]}